      "y": 73.81999999999994,
      "w": 304.6800000000002,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "a rank of “Lecturer”, “Senior Lecturer”, or “Professorial Lecturer” (UP Faculty Manual)."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 113.77999999999997,
      "w": 428.2940000000002,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 3 A lecturer is a faculty member who has earned units and"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 129.7399999999999,
      "w": 304.72800000000007,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "is currently pursuing MA/MS degree program"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 145.69999999999993,
      "w": 304.668,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "aligned/allied to his/her field of specialization. A senior"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 161.77999999999997,
      "w": 304.832,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "lecturer is a full-fledged MA/MS degree holder"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 177.7399999999999,
      "w": 304.7400000000001,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "aligned/allied to his/her field of specialization whose performance and accomplishments are comparable to at least an Assistant Professor I rank. A professional lecturer"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 225.6199999999999,
      "w": 304.70399999999995,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "is full-fledged PhD/EdD or other doctorate degree holder"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 241.69999999999993,
      "w": 228.02399999999997,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "whose performance and accomplishments."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 289.6099999999999,
      "w": 106.94,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "V. General Policies"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 313.6099999999999,
      "w": 428.40200000000004,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 1 All faculty members holding permanent positions/ items"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 329.56999999999994,
      "w": 304.5840000000002,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "must first be given regular WL for the semester before"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 345.6499999999999,
      "w": 304.572,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "additional teachers (under Contract of Service) will be"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 361.60999999999996,
      "w": 30.06000000000003,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "hired."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 385.60999999999996,
      "w": 428.668,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 2 Faculty members must be informed of their tentative"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 401.56999999999994,
      "w": 304.5840000000003,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "teaching loads (TL) at least one (1) week before the start of classes."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 441.54999999999995,
      "w": 428.596,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 3 The percentage distribution of job function vis- à-vis major"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 457.50999999999993,
      "w": 304.764,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "thrusts of the University shall be specified in the Individual"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 473.4699999999999,
      "w": 249.35600000000002,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Performance Commitment and Review (IPCR)."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 497.4699999999999,
      "w": 428.35400000000016,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 4 A faculty member with a WL & TL in excess of 30"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 513.43,
      "w": 304.8860000000001,
      "h": 12.000000000000114,
      "text": "hours/week within office hours, after office hours on a scheduled workday, on a rest day or scheduled day off, holiday, or special non-working day shall be entitled to an honorarium/ overtime pay for the teaching overload subject to the availability of funds or is granted service credit equivalence."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 617.38,
      "w": 428.4620000000001,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 5 All other assignments with monetary remuneration shall"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 633.3399999999999,
      "w": 200.65200000000002,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "not be given any workload equivalent."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 657.3399999999999,
      "w": 428.48199999999997,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 6 The IGP Manual of the University shall be used as guide"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 673.42,
      "w": 304.7160000000001,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "when a faculty member is involved in Production function."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 697.3,
      "w": 428.42600000000016,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 7 A faculty member must satisfy the mandatory functions"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 713.38,
      "w": 169.41599999999997,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "before accepting optional loads."
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 90.024,
      "y": 737.256,
      "w": 428.30600000000004,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "Section 8 In the exigency of the service, additional loads may be"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Text",
      "x": 213.77,
      "y": 753.336,
      "w": 258.68399999999997,
      "h": 12.0,
      "text": "given to faculty with more than the minimum WL."
    }
  ]
